== TECH STACK REFERENCE ==

Control Plane: Rust (axum, tokio, sqlx), REST + SSE, PostgreSQL
Workers: Rust (tokio, reqwest, git2); agent via Claude Code or Cursor CLI
CLI: Rust (clap), SSE for tail and attach
Web UI: React + TypeScript, Vite, TanStack Query, SSE for log/session stream
Logging: JSON; dual-write (local files + central DB); SSE for tail
Auth: API key (CLI, Web, workers); TLS for all connections

== API TYPES (from Rust api-types crate) ==

### ID Types (all string-based)
- SessionId, JobId, WorkerId, TaskId, PersonaId, IdentityId, ApiKeyId

### Enums
- WorkflowType: "chat" | "loop_n" | "loop_until_sentinel" | "inbox"
- SessionStatus: "pending" | "running" | "completed" | "failed"
- WorkerStatus: "idle" | "busy"
- WorkerConnectionStatus: "active" | "stale"
- TaskCompleteStatus: "completed" | "failed"
- LogLevel: "debug" | "info" | "warn" | "error"
- BranchMode: "main" | "pr"
- AgentCli: "claude_code" | "cursor"

### Key Types
- PaginatedResponse<T>: { items: T[], next_cursor?: string }
- ApiError: { code, message, details? }
- HealthResponse: { status }
- IdleResponse: { idle, pending_or_assigned_jobs }
- SessionSummary: { session_id, repo_url, workflow, status, created_at, updated_at?, retain_forever? }
- SessionDetail: extends SessionSummary + params?, persona_id?, identity_id?, jobs[]
- JobSummary: { job_id, status, created_at, error_message?, pull_request_url? }
- SessionParams: { prompt?, n?, sentinel?, agent_cli?, model?, branch_mode?, branch_name_prefix? }
- CreateSessionRequest: { repo_url, ref?, workflow, params?, persona_id?, identity_id?, retain_forever? }
- SendInputRequest: { message }
- WorkerSummary: { worker_id, host, labels?, status, last_seen_at?, connection_status? }
- WorkerDetail: extends WorkerSummary + capabilities?, client_version?, created_at
- LogEntry: { id, timestamp, level, session_id, job_id, worker_id?, source, message }
- IdentityStatus: { has_git_token, has_agent_token }
- AuthStatus: { git_token_status, git_provider?, token_expires_at?, message? }
- UpdateIdentityRequest: { agent_token?, git_token?, refresh_token? }
- RepositoryInfo: { full_name, clone_url }
- RepositoryListResponse: { items: RepositoryInfo[], provider }
- PersonaDetail: { persona_id, name, prompt, created_at, updated_at? }
- PersonaSummary: { persona_id, name, created_at }
- CreateApiKeyRequest: { label }
- CreateApiKeyResponse: { id, key, label, created_at }
- ApiKeySummary: { id, label, created_at }
- SessionEvent: { event_type, session_id, job_id?, timestamp, message? }

== API ROUTES (from server crate) ==

### Public Routes
- GET /health -> HealthResponse
- GET /ready -> HealthResponse (with DB check)
- GET /health/idle -> IdleResponse
- POST /api-keys/bootstrap -> CreateApiKeyResponse (only when no keys exist)
- GET /auth/github -> redirect to GitHub OAuth
- GET /auth/github/callback -> exchange code for token
- GET /auth/gitlab -> redirect to GitLab OAuth
- GET /auth/gitlab/callback -> exchange code for token

### Authenticated Routes (require API key via Authorization: Bearer or X-API-Key)
Sessions:
- POST /sessions -> { session_id, status, web_url }
- GET /sessions -> PaginatedResponse<SessionSummary> (query: cursor, limit, status)
- GET /sessions/:id -> SessionDetail
- PATCH /sessions/:id -> 204 (body: UpdateSessionRequest)
- DELETE /sessions/:id -> 204
- POST /sessions/:id/input -> { accepted: true } (body: SendInputRequest)
- PATCH /sessions/:sid/jobs/:jid -> 204

Workers:
- POST /workers/register -> RegisterWorkerResponse
- GET /workers -> PaginatedResponse<WorkerSummary> (query: cursor, limit)
- GET /workers/:id -> WorkerDetail
- POST /workers/:id/heartbeat -> { ok: true }
- DELETE /workers/:id -> 204

Tasks:
- POST /workers/tasks/pull -> PullTaskResponse | 204
- POST /workers/tasks/:id/complete -> { ok: true }

Logs:
- POST /workers/tasks/:id/logs -> { accepted: true }
- GET /sessions/:id/logs -> PaginatedResponse<LogEntry> (query: limit, cursor, job_id, level, last)
- DELETE /sessions/:id/logs -> 204 (query: job_id)

SSE Streams:
- GET /sessions/:id/events -> SSE (event: session_event)
- GET /sessions/:id/logs/stream -> SSE (events: log, session_event; query: job_id, level)

API Keys:
- POST /api-keys -> CreateApiKeyResponse
- GET /api-keys -> PaginatedResponse<ApiKeySummary>
- DELETE /api-keys/:id -> 204

Identities:
- GET /identities/:id -> IdentityStatus
- PATCH /identities/:id -> 204 (body: UpdateIdentityRequest)
- GET /identities/:id/auth-status -> AuthStatus
- GET /identities/:id/repositories -> RepositoryListResponse (query: provider)

Auth:
- Authorization: Bearer <api_key> or X-API-Key: <api_key>
- CORS: GET, POST, PATCH, DELETE, OPTIONS; Headers: Authorization, Content-Type, X-API-Key

